  "remarks": "Head of penal colony IK-9 in Gorki, responsible for inhumane treatment of D. Dashekevich, including tortures and denial of access to legal representatives. Lopatko had a key position in the penal colony where Dashekevich was held and where psychological pressure, including denial of sleep and isolation, was applied to political prisoners including Mr Dashekevich.",
